%% Diagram: setImmediate vs setTimeout(0) ordering inside vs outside an I/O callback
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  participant App as Script
  participant Poll as poll phase
  participant Check as check phase
  participant Timers as timers phase

  Note over App,Timers: Outside any I/O callback (non-deterministic)
  App->>Timers: schedule setTimeout 0ms
  App->>Check: schedule setImmediate
  App->>Poll: enter loop
  Poll-->>Timers: enter if 1ms threshold elapsed first
  Poll-->>Check: enter immediate fires
  Note right of Check: Order varies by startup speed

  Note over App,Timers: Inside an I/O callback (deterministic)
  App->>Poll: fs.readFile path with ioCb
  Poll->>Poll: ioCb queues setTimeout 0 plus setImmediate
  Poll->>Check: enter setImmediate fires first
  Check->>Timers: enter setTimeout fires after
  Note right of Timers: setImmediate ALWAYS first
